ityākāṃkṣā paraṃ cittaṃ sa ānando ’graṇīriva || iti ||5|| mahārūpo mahākāyo mahāvoṃ mahā vapuḥ | mahānāmā mahodāro mahāvipulamaṇḍalaḥ ||6|| 
mahārupeti | idānīṃ paramānandaprabhedā dayante| tata( tatra) mahārūpa iti hṛdaye keṣāṃcinmatena maṇimadhye mahadrūpaṃ sukhasaṃkalpaprapañco yasya sa tathā | mahāsukha prakṛtitvena traaidhātukavyāpakadharmarājyābhiṣekarūpatvāt | ata eva mahākāyaḥ prabhāsvaratvena saṃbhogakāyatvāt | anena padadvayena kāyaparamānandaḥ kathitaḥ| sambhogālokakaraṇānmahāvoṃ 'lokottaravarṇa ityarthaḥ| prakṛtiprabhāsvaratayā mahāvavibhurityarthaḥ| anena padadvayena - vāparamānanda uktaḥ| paramarahasyatayā nāmamātrasyātikamāt mahānāmā sukhasyaaudāryā 
nmahodāraḥ| ābhyāṃ caṃ ‘padāyāṃ cittaparamānanda udīritaḥ| mahāvipulamiti | vistīrṇaṃ 1 maṇḍaṃ sukhaṃ sāraṃ 12lātoti mahāvipulamaṇḍalaḥ| māyopamaprabhāsvarasukhatvena jagadvyāpanādanena jñānaparamānandaḥ| iti svapnāvasthā vidhvaṃsena saṃbhogakāyasya catvāraḥ paramānandāḥ| uktañca 
