iti vajradhātumahāmaṇḍalagāthāścaturdaśa | mahāvidyottameti | mahāvidyā mahāmudrā "tayā uttamo nityānugatatvāt | nāthaḥ svāmī| mahā mantraṃ mahāsukhaṃ jñānaṃ tenottamo niravadyaḥ, tadrūpa ityarthaḥ| ata eva gururanyeṣā miti sukhamayajñānopadeśāt | mahāyānaṃ mahāsukhajñānaṃ nīyate prāpyate aneneti mahāyānam, nayo vajrapadmavaraṭakaśikharastamārūḍhaḥ prāptaḥ sahajānandarūpa ityarthaḥ | mahāyānanaye pūrvokta uttamaścaturthadhyāna"koṭirityarthaḥ || 14 || 
