dṛśyate sarvaloke’smin pratītyotpādameva tad || iti ||5|| advayo’dvayavādī ca bhūtakoṭivyavasthitaḥ | naairātmyasiṃha"nirṇādī "kutīyaṃmṛgabhīkaraḥ ||6|| 
advayeti | advayaḥ sukhaśukrādvaaidharūpaḥ, tadrūpaprakāśanādadvayavādī| bhūtaṃ yathābhūta jñānama, tadanubhavasthānasya maṇivaraṭakasya koṭi: śikharaṃ tatra vyavasthitaḥ asthāna yogena susthitaḥ | naairātmyaṃ sarvadharmāṇāṃ nirābhāsalakṣaṇaṃ viśvabimbarūpaṃ tadeva siṃho 
