vajrabhaairavabhīkaraḥ ||25|| krodharāṭ ṣaṇmukho bhīmaḥ ṣaṇnetraḥ ṣaḍbhujo balī| 
daṃṣṭrākarālaḥ kaṅkālo halāhalaḥ śatānanaḥ ||1|| 
idānīṃ vajrabhaairavabhīkara ityādipādena sārddhadaśaślokyā ādarśajñānasya vyākhyānamāha- vajramavadhūtī, tasyā anantare( antare ) 'bhaairambha vāyurayā( vā ) danāhatādutthitātsukhamayarūpādiskandhatayā mahāsukhasvabhāvo "dṛṣṭivikalpānāṃ bhiyamabhāvaṃ karotīti vajrabhaairavabhīkaraḥ || 25 || 
krodharāḍiti | krodharāṭ viramānandādanantaraṃ rājata iti krodharāṭ | mahāsukha svabhāvo mañjuśrīrūpaḥ| ṣaṇmukhāni upāyabhūtāni pratyāhārādi ṣaṇmukhāni yasya sa tathā| sarvaduḥkhacchedakatvena bhīmaḥ| skandhadhātvāyatanendriyaviṣayakarmendriyāṇā manta hitatvāt | ākāśamiva svacchatvena ṣaṇnetrāṇi ṣaḍabhijñāsvabhāvāni yasya sa ṣaṇnetraḥ | ṣaḍviṣayānmahāsukhasvabhāvatayā bhukta iti ṣaḍbhujaḥ | mahārāgātmakajñānena skandhādi vedhasāmarthyād balī | 'bhraṣṭā caṇḍālī tasyā gurūpadeśāt jvalitāyāḥ 'śikharabhūtatvād draṣṭākarālaḥ| kaṃ sukhaṃ kalayatīti kaṅkālaḥ | halāhala ākāśajñānatayā vajrāntaḥ prāṇabandhaḥ tena] sakalanāḍīgatasukhatayā śatamanantāni nanāni sukhajñānāni yasya sa halāhalaśatānanaḥ||1|| 
yamāntako "vighnarājo vajravego bhayaṅkaraḥ | vighuṣṭavajro hṛdajro māyāvatrī mahodaraḥ ||2|| 
yamāntaketi | yamaṃ dvayaṃ svaparābhiniveśastasyāntako yuganaddhavāhītyarthaḥ| vighno māraḥ, svacittaprasaraḥ "māraḥ svacittaṃ na paro’sti māraḥ" iti | tadvināśena rājata iti . vighnarāṭ | vacasya samyag jñānasya vegaḥ prasaraḥ tadrapatvāttathā| nādabindvekīkaraṇena sakalavikalpakavalanād līkaraṇād) bhayaṅkaraḥ| anantaroktakrameṇa śūnyatākaruṇayora 
