amṛtakaṇikāsahitā catuḥhūṃkārarūpacaturānandacaturdhyānarūpeṇa oḍiyāna-jālandhara-pullīramalaya-marusañcārād bajrahūṃkārahūṃkṛtiḥ||5|| 
vajrabāṇāyudhadharo vajrakhaḍgo nikṛntanaḥ | 
viśvavajradharo vajī ekavatrī raṇajahaḥ ||6|| vajrabāṇeti | avadhūtībāṇavajreṇa nāsārandhradvayanirodhād vajamavadhūtī, tadeva bāṇāyudhaṃ taddhāraṇā vanabāṇāyudhadharaḥ| mahāsukhādhāratayā bajramadvayajñānameva khaṅgaḥ sarva kleśaniṣūdanatvādyasya sa tathā| ata eva paramavāsanāṃ nikṛntatīti nikṛntanaḥ| pañca varṇaprāṇādivāyurviśvavajram | taduktam 
pañcajñānamayaṃ śvāsaṃ pañcabhūtasvabhāvakam | niścārya yannāsāgre piṇḍarūpeṇa kalpayet || pañcavarṇamahāratnaṃ prāṇāyāma iti sthi(smatam | svamantrahṛdaye dhyātvā cittaṃ bindugataṃ nyaset || 
(gu0 ta0 18.146-148) nāsāgre sarṣapaṃ nāma prāṇāyāmasya kalpanā| prāṇāyāme sthitāḥ pañcaraśmayo buddhabhāṣitāḥ|| pañcavarṇamayaṃ śvāsaṃ prāṇāyāmasya kalpanā| nāsikāgne prayatnena bhāvayedyogavit sadā || iti | 
bhedādanāhatadharmadhāturūpatayā vidhuṣṭamahāśabdo vajramabhedyamasya, tena vā abhedyaḥ, sa tathā| sahajakāyatvāt hṛdvajaḥ| māyā manovivā(tta) vajro’bhedyatvādyasya sa tathā| dharmadhātu rūpatayā sakalabhāvakroḍīkaraṇād mahodaraḥ||2|| 
kuliśeśo vajrayonivajramaṇḍo nabhopamaḥ | 'acalaaikajaṭāṭopo gajacarmapaṭādhṛk ||3|| 
kuliśeśeti | kuliśe vajrarandhradvayābhyantare oḍiyāne jālandharasaṃjñake mahāsukha svabhāvena īśvaratvāt | tathā vajrāṇāṃ sarvatathāgatakāyavācittajñānavajrāṇāṃ yoni rutpattisthānaṃ sahajānandotpattitvāt | teṣāṃ divyasukhāsvādarūpatvādvava bhaṇḍo’bhedya sāraḥ| nirāvaraṇatayā sarvākāravaropetaśūnyatāsvabhāvatvānnabhopamaḥ| niścalīkṛtaprāṇa tvādacalaḥ, sarvasamarasobhāvāvekajaṭāyā ivāṭopa āḍambaro yasya sa tathā| divyamudrā prayogeṇa mahāsukharūpatayā dha[ dhātu ]paryantagataśukra śvetagajacarma paṭā sahaja tvāttattādātmyena dharatīti tathā ||3|| 
hāhākāro mahāghoro hīhīkāro bhayānakaḥ | 
