ācāryoṃ guhyaprajñā ca 'caturthaṃ phala rūpatā| tadeteṣu kathaṃ nāma mahānto vipratipedire || paramaviramayormadhya lakṣa(kṣyaṃ) ye prati jānate| śabdasya saṃgatiṃ yatnātkurvanti yadi nāma "te || na teṣāmiha seko’yaṃ caturthoṃ ghaṭate punaḥ| tṛtīyaṃ phalarūpatvād niṣpannaṃ 'cetsvarūpataḥ || 'ādaau kāryasya niṣpattyā paścāddhetunātra kim | 
seko’yaṃ darśita[sta ]sya siddhayarthaṃ nānyahetunā || tasya cedagrataḥ siddhiḥ kimarthaṃ sa punarbhavet | phalasya yadi niṣpattī paścātseko’bhidhīyate || āśvāsa-prabhedo’tra buddhavaja dharayoḥ katham | pūrvavadharāśvāsaḥ paścād buddhasya ced bhavet || evaṃ hetoḥ phalasyāpi 11vyaktatā kena 12vāryate | gāthāyā anurodhena dvayormadhye bhavedyadi || 13lakṣyaṃ naaivānyathārthatvād gāthāyā iva tattvataḥ| lakṣyasyaaivānurodhena gāthārtho yujyate punaḥ || na hi gāthānurodhena lakṣyamanyatraḥ nīyate| śrīsamāje’tha hevane bhedo nāstīha tattvataḥ || sādhanasya tu bhedena bhedāstatropaṇitāḥ| tatra sekāstridhā proktā iti cellokata"stu saḥ|| lokottarābhiṣekastu prokto’pi na sphuṭīkṛtaḥ| prajñājñānābhiṣekeṇa jñātavyaḥ sa caturthakaḥ | ityevaṃ nipuṇaṃ jñātuṃ sevitavyo hi sadguruḥ | tasmāt kadācitsaṃgatyā 1"lakṣyaṃ madhye vadanti ye|| 
