kumbho guhyābhiṣekastu prajñā jñānābhiṣekataḥ| punareva mahāmudrā tasyā jñānābhidhānakaḥ || . kṣara:(roja)kṣarastataḥ "spando nispandaśca tato’paraḥ| kāyavāñcittasaṃśuddhayā abhiṣekatrayaṃ kramāt || caturtho jñānasaṃśuddhiḥ kāyavāñcitta śodhakaḥ| . bālaḥ praauḍha stathāvṛddhaścaturthastu prajāpatiḥ || | prajñāstanāṅgasaṃsparśī bodhicittacyutaṃ sukham | payodharābhiṣiktaḥ sa bālaḥ 'prokto yataḥ sukham || guhyasphālāccirājjñānaṃ jātaṃ) bodhicittacyutaṃ sukham| . praauḍha़o guhyābhiṣiktaḥ sa guhyātprāpto yataḥ sukham || guhyāsphālacirājjātaṃ vajrāne spandataḥ sukham | prajñājñānābhiṣiktaḥ sa vṛddhaḥ spandaṃ gato yataḥ|| mahāmudrānurāgād yajjātaṃ nispandataḥ sukham | 
