amṛtakaṇikāsahitā 
āryamañjuśrīnāmasaṅgītiḥ anābhogena pañcakāmopabhogasukhatvānirgata ābhogo vikalpapravṛttirasya sa tathā| uktañca-"pūrvapraṇidhānā hitasatatānābhogavāhi parakāryam" iti | 
divārātrisaṃdhyāsamādhitrayabhedena triṣu adhvasu saṃbhūtāḥ kāyavāñcittanirmāṇa saṃbhogadharmakāyākhyā buddhāsteṣāṃ kārya sattvārtharūpamahāsukhānubhavanaṃ karotīti tathā || 23 || 
anādinidhano buddha · ādibuddho niranvayaḥ| jñānekacakṣuramalo . . jñānamūrtistathāgataḥ ||24|| 
anādīti| dharmadhātujñānarūpatvena na. vidyete ādinidhane utpādanirodhī viramakṣaṇacyutikṣaṇī yasya sa tathā| sarvapadārthānāṃ samatayā vagamād buddhaḥ| sāṃkle śikavayavadānikadharmāṇāṃ paramārthato’bhāvenākāro niṣedhārthaḥ | tenādibuddhaḥ| ekakṣaṇa pañcākāraviṃśatyākāramāyājālābhisambodhilakṣaṇaṃ sukhamādibuddha ityarthaḥ| nirasto ’nvayaḥ prajñopāyātmako grāhyagrāhakalakṣaṇo dharmo yena sa tathā| jñānamadvaya jñānaṃ tadevekadvitīyaṃ cakṣussarvadharmasukhaśitvādyasya sa tathā | sakalavikalpapahīṇatvā damalaḥ| jñānaṃ śanyatājñānaṃ tadeva mūttiḥ sahajasukhāvabhāso yasya sa tathā | tathā tathatā kamādamudrā tatra gatamānandādisukhajñānaṃ yasya sa tathāgataḥ ||24|| 
