amṛtakaṇikāsahitāḥ śvāsagaṇastasya pade mahāsukhapade nikṣepo layīkaraṇāṃ tenaḥ tatra vānartanaṃ sukhollāso yasya sa tathā paramākṣaraviddhaśvāsagaṇatvena śrīmacchatamadvayajñānaspharaṇānantyaṃ tad bhuṃkta iti śrīmacchatabhujo jñānakāyastasyābhogo vistāraḥ paripuṣṭirasya sa tathā| sarvabhāvānāṃ śūnyatāsvabhāvenāvabodhād gaganasyābhogo vyāpitvam | tatra mahāsukhena nartanaṃ pravarttanaṃ yasya sa.tathoktaḥ || 3|| . . . . . . . . 
