idānīmiṣṭārthasādhaka ityādinā nirāvaraṇavedanāskandharatnasambhavarūpeṇa samatā jñānamukhena tadeva sahajajñānamāha 
'iṃṣṭārthasādhakaḥ paraḥ sarvāpāyaviśodhakaḥ | ... . . sarvasattvottamo nāthaḥ sarva sattvapramocakaḥ ||1|| 
.... :: .. . . . . . . . . . 
iṣṭārthasādhaketi| sarvāśāparipūrakaparamākṣarajñānarūpatvādiṣṭa ścāsāvarthaśceti iṣṭārthaḥ, tasya sādhako niṣpādakaḥ vana padmānubhūtabindu'trayātītatvāt paraḥ| sarvāpāyasya saṃsāravāsana(nā)yā viśodhako mahāsukhaaikakartā| sarvasattvānāṃ kāyavāk cittānāmuttamo jñānakāyaḥ, ata eva nātho anāthānāṃ mahāmudrā padmaprakāśakatvena sarvasattvānāṃ pramocakaḥ ||1||. . ... . . . . . 
... kleśasaṃgrāmaśūraaikaḥ ajñānaripudarpahā | 
dhīśṛṅgāradharaḥ śrīmān vīrabībhatsarūpadhṛk ||2|| kleśasaṃgrāmeti| sarvasattvacaritakleśānāṃ samyagjñānaśastreṇa nikṛntanāt | kleśasaṃgrāme eko’dvitīyaḥ śūraḥ| ārṣatvādanyathāśabdavinyāsaḥ| ajñānaṃ avidyā saaiva ripuścyutiḥ duḥkhadāyitvāt tasya do vahivikṣepaḥ, tannirābhāsīkaraṇāvajñānaripu pahā | cittamātrasyāpi nirasanenāpagatakleśopakleśatvād ghoḥ| dharmatā saṅketena bhṛṅgāraḥ sahajānandaśukrastabāraṇāttathā| uṣṇīṣāducchalitabodhicittadhārayā sarvāṅgā pyāyanena laaukikalokottarasampattimān śrīmān | upāyasya 'karuṇāṅgatvena vīrarasatvaṃ prajñāyāḥ śūnyatāṅgatvena bobhatsarasatvaṃ tadvaaidharūpaṃ mahāsukhavīrabībhatsarūpaṃ taddharatīti tathā ||2|| 
bāhudaṇḍaśatākṣepapadanikṣepanartanaḥ | 
śrīmacchatabhujābhogagaganābhoganartanaḥ ||3|| bāhadaṇḍeti | bāhudaṇḍaḥ prāṇāpānavāyudaṇḍadvayaṃ tasya vāmadakṣiṇa nāsāpuṭadaśa maṇḍalasaṃkrāntibhedenānantyāt śatam, tasyākṣepa ākṛṣṭiḥ madhyamāpraveśena kumbhakāvasthā 
..... ekapādatalākrāntamahīmaṇḍatale sthitaḥ |Mai 
brahmāṇḍaśikharā krāntapādāṅguṣṭhanakhe sthitaḥ ||4|| ekapādeti | ekapādatalenādvitīyapratiṣṭhārūpeṇākāntaṃ sthirīkṛtamadhyasitam | mahīmaṇḍalatale. nābhyadho vajramaṇiśikhare sthitaṃ rajo bodhicittaṃ yena sa:tathā | ārṣatvā llakāre lope na nirdeśaḥ | athavā mahī śūnyatā śukrabījadhāraṇāta, tasyā maṇḍa: sāra iti yojyam | brahmāṇḍaśikharaṃ brahmarandhaṃ tadākrānto yo’saau pādāṅguṣṭhanakho viti krameṇoṣṇīṣagatavajrasaṃbandhi(bodhi)cittaṃ tatra sthito’dvaya yogena-:: 
ekaṃ padaṃ vajramaṇaau rajo’rke uṣṇīṣaśukra śaśini dvitīyam | nyastaṃ sadācchedyamabhedyamiṣṭaṃ bhartustrilokamahitaṃ śirasā praṇamya || 
... (vi0 pra0 1, pṛ0 3) bharturbodhicittavajasya śrīkālacakrādirūpasya padyate gamyate yena tatpadaṃ jñāna makṣaraṃ nyasta ābodhitam | avidyā nirodhāya vajramaṇāvapratiṣṭhitanirvāṇabhūmaau rajo’rke mahomaṇḍalatale jñānadhātaau eka padaṃ dakṣiṇamityekapādatalākrāntaḥ| uṣṇīṣabhavasukhāti krānte śukra śaśini pādāṅguṣṭhanakhe 'prākkāmakalodayātmake vijñānadhātaau 'dvitīyam | yad vāmamiti brahmāṇḍaśikharākāntaḥ| sadāḥ kālatraye, kleśāvaraṇātikrāntatvāda vidyājñānakartikayācchedyam| vijñānadharmatātītatvād grāhyagnāhakakoṭyā’bhedyam | mahāsakharūpatvādiṣṭam | “kṛtakṛtyasthale maṇaau sthitaṃ lokācārojjhitatvātriloka mahitam| saṃsārapārakoṭāvuṣṇīṣe sthitamiti | śrīādibuddhe coktam ... prāṇāyāmānalena · dravamapi śaśinaḥ pānaka madyapānam | 
uṣṇīṣe’ṅguṣṭhaparvād brajati tithivaśātpūrṇimāntaṃ svacittasa| .. uṣṇīṣādagalīṣa vrajati punaridaṃ kṛṣṇapakṣāvasāne | .. 
