tānyevotsukavanti, lendriyabalānyutleśabījānilaḥ| vandhaḥ sadgurupādapaṅkajarajaḥ sparśaḥ svayaṃ yadaśā 
detanmāmakasāramityaharahaḥ spandanti tattvāmṛtam || .. sarvadharmasvabhāvatathatāvagamācchanyatāratiḥ| ubhayāntāpātādanadhīḥ| rāga virāgamadhyarāgaprakṛtivigamād bhavarāgādyatītaḥ| bhavatraye kāyavāñcittekalolobhāve mahāsukhe mahatī yā prākṛtamayī ratirasya sa tathā || 6 || - śuddhaḥ śubhrābhradhavalaḥ śaraccandrāṃśusuprabhaḥ | | . bālākamaṇḍalacchāyo mahārāganakhaprabhaḥ ||7|| .. 
śuddhaśubheti | vajrasattva svarūpatvenāvidyāmalavigamācchuddhaḥ| śaradabhraśubhratvā 'dviśuddhasarvadhātudravatvācca śubhrābhradhavalaḥ | vāsanāmātrasyāpyabhāvāccharaccandrāṃśuvaccho bhanā prabhā yasya sa tathā| mahārāgānagataḥ prāṇāpānādvayasaṃghadravaśāttadātmīyaṃ cittaṃ bālārkamaṇḍalavadābhāsata iti bālārkamaṇḍalasyevacchāyā- kāntiryasya sahajacaṇḍālī. jyotiṣāśliṣṭatvādvā | mahāsukhena pādāṅgaṣṭhe nakhaparyantavyāpanād mahārāgasya nakhaparyantaṃ teṣu prabhā chāyā sukhavyāptirasya bodhicittarājasya sa tathā ||7|| 
