āryamañjuśrīnāmasaṅgītiḥ 
amṛtakaṇikāsahitā nāḍītvaṃ pañcame yāti 'asthitāṃ yāti ṣaṣṭhame| 
saptame majjatāṃ yāti saptāvattaṃ bhavediti || tathā ( tatheti )| tathatā dharmodayā avadhūtī tadgatatvena sarvaguṇodayāddaśavidha prāṇādivāyunirodhena daśabhūmisamantaprabhāparyantaphalabhūmiṃ prāptaḥ tathāgataḥ| sa eva guṇovadhiḥ sarvabhūmyāśrayatvena tattara sattvārthakaraṇāt | antargatākāśamaṇḍalatvena vāma dakṣiṇanāsāpuṭayoḥ prāṇavāhamaṇḍalānyaṣṭaau teṣāṃ mārgo madhyamāpraveśastanlayaṃ tadupadeśa gurupadiṣṭapratyāhārādinā vettīti tathā| samyaksaṃbuddhaḥ svayaṃbhūḥ jñānī tasya mārgoṃ dharmadhātujñānaṃ tatsākṣātkārāttathā || 10 || 
sarvasattvamahāsaṅgo niḥsaṅgo gaganopamaḥ | 
sarvasattvamano jātaḥ sarvasattvamanojavaḥ ||11|| 
sarva [sattveti]| dharmakāyābhinnanirmāṇakāyena sarvasattvārthāparityāgāta sarvasattveṣu mahānāsaṅgaḥ pācanādinā yasya sa tathā| śūnyatā svabhāvena nissanaḥ| vikalpa lepābhāvena gaganopamaḥ| prakṛtiprabhāsvaratvamanasikāreṇa sarvasatsvānāṃ manasi jātatvāttathā| sarvasattveṣvadhimuktivaśena vajradharādipratibhāsarūpatvāt sarvasattva manojavaḥ ||11|| 
sarvasattvendriyārthajñaḥ sarvasattvamanoharaḥ | 
pañcaskandhārthatattvajñaḥ pañcaskandhaviśuddhadhṛk ||12|| sarvasattvendriyeti | sarvasatvānāṃ madumadhyādhimātrarūpāṇīndriyāṇi teṣāmarthaḥ 'saprapañcaniṣprapañcamavyāhatamahāsukhasamādhinā jānātīti tathā| sarvasatvānāṃ manāṃsi vikalpacittāni harati tāni niḥsvabhāvīkaroti (tīti) sarvasattvamanoharaḥ| pañcasphandhārthatvaṃ pāramārthikavajeṇa sarvatathāgatavyūhasya tathatāyāṃ praveśastajjñānāttathā | uktañca 
rūpaskandhagatādarśa bhūdhātunayanendriyam | 
rūpaṃ ca pañcamaṃ yāti krodhamaaitreyasaṃyutam || ityādi | prabhāsvarotthānāt ] prakṛtiprabhāsvaratāṃ pañcaskandhārthaṃ viśuddhaṃ dharatīti pañcaskandhaviśuddhadhak || 12|| 
