uktañca 
skandhadhātvādike dagdhe pañcamaṇḍalavāhake| viṣayendriyaniruddha cānandāce samucchite || sāvati ( yati ) bindukānindo hūṃkāro mūnisaṃsthitaḥ| lalāṭe candrataḥ sūrye kaṇṭhāddravo tato hṛdi | nābhaau caṇḍālikāviṣṭaṃ guhya cakre tato gataṃ || sampāto guhyacakre’sminkathito’yaṃ mahāpaśuḥ || "trisṛkādhastrināḍīnāṃ patracandraṃ pradarśitam | saptajanmā paśuścaaiva khecarīsiddhidāyakaḥ || mūcchito harate vyādhi 'harati (jārito) skandhadhātukam | dadāti cakravattittvaṃ viṣayendriyamāritaḥ khecaratvaṃ dadātyeṣo’ṇimādiguṇaairyutaḥ| kṣipraṃ dadāti buddhatvaṃ ja(mā)raṇādyaairanu sāritaḥ|| 'bāhyāmṛto yathā baddhastathājñānaraso’pyayam | 
dadāti vipulāṃ siddhi sarvaduḥkhāpahāriṇīm || evaṃ brahmā paśurviṣṇurguhyacakre nipātitaḥ| dadāti vipulaṃ hyāyuryāvadā hadi(huti)saṃplavam || urcerāhuḥ paśuḥ proktaścandrasūryaau mahāpaśūḥ| 
pātitā brahmarandhreṇa bhuktimuktiphalapradāḥ|| raktasnāyustathā majjā pātanīyaḥ prayatnataḥ| ete ca paśavo jñeyā nānyabāhye’stu "dehinām || saptājanmāsta sarveṣāṃ paśanāṃ parameśvaraḥ| saptajanmā yathā dehe tathā vakṣyāmi tacchṛṇu || annapānarasaṃ sarvaṃ bhaktaṃ pītañca ṣaḍavidham | pākato rasatāṃ yāti prathamaṃ janma tasya tat || paścād rudhiratāṃ yāti dvitīyaṃ bhavati sphuṭam | 
