āryamanjuśrīnāmasaṅgītiḥ sarva niryāṇakoṭisthaḥ sarvanirmāṇakovidaḥ | 
sarvaniryāṇamārgasthaḥ sarvaniryāṇadeśakaḥ ||13|| sarvaniryāṇeti| sarvaniryāṇakoṭo yuganaddhasamādhaau sthitatvāttathā| avācya naairātmyaṃ sukhavedakatvāt sarvaniryāṇakovidaḥ| mahāsukharatnatvena niḥsaṅgatve’pi mahākaruṇābalena śrāvakādimārge sthitatvāt sarvaniryāṇamārgasthaḥ| mahāsukhakāya dharmeṇa dharmadhātuḥ sarvanirmāṇaṃ tasya deśa ko’vikalpena prakāśakaḥ || 13 || 
dvādaśāṅgabhavotkhāto dvādaśākāraśuddhadhṛk | 
catuḥsatyanayākāraḥ aṣṭajñānāvabodhadhṛk ||14|| dvādaśāṅgeti| avidyādidvādaśāṅganirodhena pīṭhopapīṭhādisthānamahāsukhatvena vādvādaśāṅgabhavotkhātaḥ| uktañca 
parapīṭheti prajñoktā ātmapīṭhamupāyakam| anayoradvayībhāvo yogapīṭha iti smṛtam || tatvapīṭhaṃ tadutpannaṃ tadrahitaṃ ca yad bhavet | sahajeti samākhyātaṃ vākpathātītagocaram || iti | 
amṛtakaṇikāsahitā dvādaśākārasatyārthaḥ ṣoḍaśākāratattvavit | 
viṃśatyākārasaṃbodhivibuddhaḥ' sarvavit paraḥ ||15|| dvādaśākāreti | niḥspa(sya)ndavipākapuruṣa (ṣā)kāravaaimalyakṣaṇānāṃ pratyeka guṇyād dvādaśākārā dvādaśabhumayaḥ saṃvṛtiparamārthasatyābhedena tadyogād dvādaśākāra. 'satyārthaḥ| tatra kāyavākacittavivekaniḥspa(sya)ndabhedena prathamaṃ trika nirmāṇakāyasya | bhāsa-pratibhāsa-prakṛtinirābhāsavipākabhedena dvitīyaṃ trikaṃ saṃbhogakāyasya | cittacaaita sikāvidyāpuruṣa (ṣā)kāra[vaaimalyavipākā bhedena tṛtīyaṃ trikaṃ dharmakāyasya | ānanda dvayaviramasahajānandavaaimalyabhedena caturthatrika jñānakāyasyeti | prāṇakṣayeṇa rajo nirodhādvā nirodhitameṣavṛṣādidvādaśarāśitvena vā dvādaśabhūmilābhād dvādaśākārasatyārthaḥ | ṣoḍaśānanda kalā śukranirodhena ṣoḍaśākāratattva vattīta tathā| sāṃsārikaṣoḍaśakalā [kṣayato’]kṣaratvāt ṣoḍaśākāratattvavit | ṣaḍaṅgabhāvanayā viśuddhāvadhūtīviśuddhatvena pañcaskandha-pañcadhātu-pañcendriya-pañcāyatanaviśuddhayākārāvabodhād viśatyākāra sambodhiḥ | avidyānirodhād vibuddhaḥ| sarvabuddhamaya bhāvanāmāvabodhāt sarvavit || 15 || 
ameyabuddhanirmāṇakāyakoṭivibhāvakaḥ | 
sarvakṣaṇābhisamayaḥ sarvacittakṣaṇārthavit ||16|| ameyeti | sarvanirvāṇakalolībhūtāprameyabuddhanirmāṇarūpabhāvagrāmasya śvāsasamūhasya mahāsukhatvenekakṣaṇe vibhāvanāttathā | anena madhya nimittamuktam | pratiśvāsaṃ sarvaśvāsānāṃ mahāsukhena bodhāt sarvakṣaṇābhisamayaḥ| sarvasattvānāṃ cittakṣaṇānāṃ ca mahāsukhatveneva vettīti tathā || 16 || . 
nānāyānanayopāyajagadarthavibhāvakaḥ | 
yānatritayaniryāta ekayānaphale sthitaḥ ||17|| nānāyāneti | nānāyānanayopāyena caturaṅga-ṣaḍaṅgabinduyogādinā jagadayaṃ mahāsukhatvena vibhāvayati sphārayatīti tathā| jñānakāyatvena kāyavākacittaniryā tatvād yānatri tayaniryātaḥ | ekamadvitīyaṃ yānaṃ phalaṃ haṃkārāstatra sthitaḥ || 17 || 
kleśadhātu viśuddhātmā karmadhātukṣayaṅkaraḥ | 
