jñānaskandhavijñānaskandhajñānadhātvākāśadhātumanaḥśrotraśabdadharmadhātudivyendriyabhaga mūtrasrāvaśukracyutirūpāṇāṃ nirāvaraṇatā pratyekaṃ svasva viṣayagrahaṇavivajitatvaṃ samarasa mekalolībhūtatvaṃ para(pratha)mākṣaraśūnyaṃ yogisvasaṃvedyas, na sarvābhāvalakṣaṇam | tadevāha-tamā kāraśūnyaṃ rekhāmātramanuccārya kartṛkākāraṃ madhye, saṃskāraskandhavāyudhātughrāṇasparśa vāgindriyavisāvāṇāmekalolībhūtatvaṃ madhyānāhatacihnāt pūrveṇa, ikāraśūnyaṃ daṇḍākāraṃ dvitīyākṣaraśūnyam | vedanāskandhatejodhātucakṣurasapāṇigatīnāṃ nirāvara ṇatā madhyā nāhatacihāikṣiṇena lūkāraśūnyaṃ bindudvayaṃ tṛtīyākṣaraśanyam | saṃjñāskandhatoyadhātujihvā rūpapādendriyādānānāṃ nirāvaraṇatā madhyānāhatacihnādvāmena, bindurūpamekamanuccāryamūkāra śūnyaṃ caturthākṣaramahāśūnyam | rūpaskandhapṛthivīdhātukāyendriyagandhapāyvālāpānāṃ samarasa tvamekalolībhūtatvaṃ, madhyānāhatacihnāt paścimena, tad "halākṛtiḥ ekāraśūnyaṃ pañcākṣara śūnyam | evaṃ vaṃkāraḥ pañcākṣaro mahāśūnyo nirālambakaruṇātmakaḥ, paramāṇudharmatātīta: pratisenātulyo yogigamyaḥ, tadādhārabhūta ekāro dharmodayarūpaḥ sarvākāraśūnyatāsvabhāvo binduśūnyaḥ ṣaḍakṣaraḥ | tathāhi-vijñānaskandha ākāśadhātuśrotradharmadhātubhagaśukracyutīnāṃ nirāvaraṇaśūnyatā| pūrvoktā madhyānāhatacihnasyorce kavargātmakaṃ kakāravyañjanamarnuccārya prathamaṃ binduśūnyam | saṃskāraskandhavāyudhātughrāṇendriyasparśavāg"visāvāṇāṃ nirāvaraṇa sarvākāraśūnyatā | pūrvoktacihnasya pūrva cavargātmakaṃ cakāravyañjanamanuccārya [ dvitīyaṃ ] binduśūnyam| vedanāskandhatejodhātucakṣurasapāṇīndriyagatīnāṃ sarvākāranirāvaraṇa śūnyatā| dakṣiṇacihnasya dakṣiṇe ṭavargātmakaṃ ṭakāravyañjanamanuccārya tṛtīyaṃ bindu śūnyam | saṃjñāskandhatoyadhātujihvārūpapādendriyādānānāṃ nirāvaraṇaśūnyatā | uttaracihna syottare pavargātmaka pakāravyañjanamanuccārya caturthabinduśūnyam | rūpaskandhapṛthivīdhātu kāyendriyagandhapāyavālāpānāṃ nirāvaraṇaśūnyatā| paścimacihnasya paścime tavargātmakaṃ takāravyañjanamanuccārya pañcamaṃ binduśūnyam | jñānaskandhajñānadhātumanaḥśabdadivyendriya mūtrasrāvāṇāṃ sarvākāranirāvaraṇaśūnyatā| madhyānāhatacihnasyādhastāt śavargātmakaṃ śakāravyañjanamanuccārya ṣaṣṭhaṃ binduśūnyamiti | evaṃ binduśūnyaḥ ṣaḍakṣaro dharmodayaḥ | kuliśadhara ekāraḥ śūnyatā sālambā pratisenāsvarūpiṇīti | etena pañcākṣaro mahā śūnyaḥ | svarasamūhaḥ [śukra] candra ityucyate| binduśūnyaḥ ṣaḍakṣaro vyañjanasamūho rajaḥ sūrya ityucyate | atra ca śukra candro vaṃkāro vacaṃ, rajaḥ sūrya ekāraḥ padmam, anayorvajra padmayorekatvaṃ vajra sattva iti | vacaṃ paramasukhaṃ, jñānaṃ śukra, 'sattvaḥ sarvākāraprajñābimba jñeyamiti | jñānavijñānādhiṣṭhitaṃ nirāvaraṇamekalolī bhūtatvaṃ jagadarthakārī vanasattva iti | etacca vimalaprabhāyām ( bhāga-1, pṛ0 47-50 ) uktaṃ jñeyamiti ||2|| 
