anālambā kṛpā paścājjagadarthakarī phalam || iti | ṣoḍaśānāṃ kalānāmarddhamaṣṭo tadarddha catvāro bindavaḥ kāyavāñcittajñānalakṣaṇāḥ, jāgratsvapnasuṣuptituryāvasthājanakāḥ| tāt dhārayatīti ṣoḍaśārddhabindudhṛk | samaya catuṣṭayapālaka vanasattvo mahārāga ityarthaḥ| akala: śuklapakṣapañcadaśakalārahitaḥ| tāsāmante sthitaḥ śuklapūrṇimāvasāne kalanātīta iti | kalanā kṛṣṇapratipat tatrā pratiṣṭhitaḥ kalanātītaḥ sahaja ityarthaḥ | caturthadhyānakoṭigiti prathamamānandasukhadhyānaṃ, dvitīyaṃ paramānandasukhadhyānaṃ, tṛtīyaṃ viramānandasukhadhyānaṃ, caturtha sahajānandasukhadhyānam | pañcamī daśamī [pañcadaśamī ] pūrṇā pūrṇānte bindī paramākṣarasukhadhyānaṃ sthitaṃ tasya koṭiragrabhāgaḥ sukhaparipūrṇatā tāṃ dharatīti caturthadhyānakoṭik || 3|| 
sarvadhyānakalābhijñaḥ samādhikula gotravit | 
