dharmadānapatiḥ śreṣṭhaścaturmudrārthadeśakaḥ | 
paryupāsyatamo jagatāṃ niryāṇatrayayāyinām ||14|| dharmavāneti yathābhavyatā(tayā ) aviparītadharmadānāda dharmadānapatiḥ | manaso’pi tyāgād dharmadānapatitvena śreṣṭhaḥ| karmamudrā-mahāmudrā-jñānamudrā-samayamudrārthasya deśaka: prakāśakaḥ | caturmudrārthaprakāśanādeva niryāṇatraya yāyināṃ bhūcarakhecaramahāmudrāsiddhi gāmināṃ jagatāṃ paryupāsyaḥ| uktañca caturmudropadeśe, tadyathā 
karmajñānamahāmudrāsamayākhyaḥ prabhāsvaraḥ| 
heturbhāvyā tathā prāpyā caturtho’vinaśvaraḥ || heturiti prathama karmamudrodbhataṃ yatsahajamacyutasukham | uktañca bhagavatā tatsatyameva, kintu saṃvṛtyā laaukikadṛṣṭāntenā darśamiva na paramārthataḥ | tasmāttīkṣṇendriyeṇa 'na grāhyā karmamudrā | karmamudrā ca stanakeśavato kāmadhātusukhasya hetuḥ | karma cumbanāliṅga naguhyasparśavatasphālanādivyāpārātmakaṃ, tenopalakṣitā mudrā pratyayakāriṇī| pratyayo’tra kṣarasukhalakṣaṇaḥ | mudaṃ sukhaviśeṣaṃ rāti dadāti iti mudrā bhāvyā | jñānamudrā, sā ca sva cittaparikalpitā viśvamātrādidevosvabhāvā pūrvānubhūtā rūpadhātusukhasya hetuḥ | jñānaṃ pūrva hasitaramitādibhāvanālakṣaṇaṃ, pratyayo’tra spandasukhalakṣaṇaḥ | skandhadhātvāyatanādidevatā kāreṇa viśodhya maṇḍalacakrasvabhāvaṃ yathā vidhinā sphuṭīkṛtya manthamanthānayogena jñāna vahni prajvālya yāvad dagdhe’haṃ sakte śaśī lalāṭakaṇṭhahunnābhivajakamalakaṇi kāgrataḥ| 
