bodhicittarūpeṇa viṣayendriyasamastamahāsukhasāgarasya yadekalolī bhūtatanmayasamādhimā panno bhūtvā tiṣṭhet yāvat śrīmahāmudrā’bhimukhī bhavatīti prāpyā| mahāmudrā svapnendrajālamano mayasadṛśī| mahatī cāso [ mudrā ] mahāmudrā ceti kṛtvā mahattvaṃ punarasyāḥ sarvākāravaro petatvaṃ na prādeśikatvam, mudrayate’neneti bodhicittavatreṇa mudrā| pratyayo’tra svacitta parikalpanādharmarahito dhūmādinimittapūrvakaḥ svacittapratibhāso yogigamyaḥ pratisenā vaditi | tāmāliṅgaya yāvatsamayamudrā sākṣāt kriyate| avinaśvarā paramākṣarasva rūpiṇī sāca phalarūpamahāmudrā| mudaṃ paramākṣarasukhalakṣaṇaṃ rāti sarvakālamā datte pūrṇāvasthāyāmacalayogeneti mudrā| mahattvaṃ cāsyāḥ prahāṇamahatvenādhigamamahattvena | yatra prahāṇamahattvaṃ 'savāsanasarvāvaraṇaprahāṇalakṣaṇa svabhāvakāyākhyaprabhāsvarasākṣāt karaṇalakṣaṇam | adhigamamahattvaṃ tu pariśuddhasarvabuddhadharmātmakayuganaddhākhya kāyasākṣāt karaṇam | yattunaḥ śaradamalamadhyāhnagagana sannibhaṃ śūnyatakarasaprabhāsvarasākṣātkāra eva sakalabuddhadharmādhigamo’śeṣaviśvārthasampādanarūpeṇa| tatra sarvabuddhadharmāṇāṃ bimbādhā mānatvāt | ata eva dharmāṇāmāśrayaḥ kāyo dharmakāya ityācakṣate| tatra ca pratibhā senāpyadhigamavyavasthāyāṃ ghaṭapratibhāse ghaṭāyadhigamo prasaṅgo dunivāraḥ kiñca sāṃkhya darśanamadūṣaṇaṃ syāt | api ca, māyāsvapnagandharvapurapratisenā'vat kalpitamaśeṣaskandhadhā tvāyatanādidarśanaṃ saṃvṛtisatyadarśanaṃ svādhiṣṭhānaṃ cocyate| saṃvṛtisatyameva paramārthasatyaṃ prabhāsvarapariśuddhamādarśādirūpaṃ vaairocanādyādheyadevatāvṛndaṃ kūṭāgārādyādhāramaṇḍalaṃ ca tadeva ca lokottaramaṇḍalatayā sarvatantrarājeṣu gīyate | samastabuddhadharmasvabhāvatayā ca tadeva satyadvayādvaaidhobhāvasvabhāvaṃ yuganaddhāsyamucyate, tasmāyuganaddhakāya eva dharmakāyaḥ sāṃbhogika svābhāvikakāyābhyāṃ pṛthagbhūto yogipratyakṣavedyaḥ | uktañca nāgārjunapādaaiḥ "yo naaiko nāpyaneka" ityādinā dharmakāyalakṣaṇam | "lokātītāmacintyām" ityā dinā sambhogakāyasya| "sattvānāṃ pākahetoḥ kvacidanala iva bhāti yo dīpyamānaḥ" ityādinā nirmāṇakāyasy