pañcatathāgatastutiḥ namaste varada vajrāgya bhūtakoṭe namo’stu te || namaste śūnyatāgarbha buddhabodhe namo’stu te ||1|| buddharāga namaste’stu buddhakāma namo namaḥ || buddhaprīte namastubhyaṃ buddhamoda namo namaḥ ||2|| buddhasmita namastubhyaṃ buddhahāsa namo namaḥ| buddhavāca namastubhyaṃ buddhabhāva namo namaḥ ||3|| abhavodbhava 'namastubhyaṃ namaste buddha saṃbhava| gaganodbhava namastubhyaṃ namaste jñāna sambhava ||4|| māyājāla namastubhyaṃ namaste buddhanāṭaka | namaste sarvasarvebhyo jñānakāya namo’stu te ||5|| 
