___ mantramukhena śruti(ta)cintābhāvanācaryā caratīti, tathā nāmnā cūḍāmaṇi: sarvatathāgatakulodbhavānāmiti nāmacūḍāmaṇiḥ| avikalabuddhaguṇayogāt saphalapari samāptā| sarvadharmārthasampūrṇāmanyūnāmakhaṇḍāmanabhibhavānāṃ( vanī )yāṃ dhārayiṣyati granthārthataḥ | vācayiṣyati maṇḍalānāṃ puraḥsaraṃ vacanāt | paryavāpsyati cintātaḥ| yoniśaśca manasi kariṣyati bhāvanātaḥ| ojaso balaṃ sāmānyamojobalaṃ tejasos praghṛṣyati tejo antaḥ sphuritam | tejomāhātmyapratyaṅgirāpratipakṣabhūtā| pañcaka ṣāyāḥ sattvadṛṣṭikalpāyuḥparisphāralakṣaṇāḥ| aślokābhyākhyānanindāvādapūrvakapratyā khyānam | priyo mana māpo manonāhī| adhiṣṭhito’na (nuvattino daśasu dikṣu dharmadundubhiryasya sa tādṛśo dharmarāja iti dharmarājādhipatirbhaviṣyatīti sambandhaḥ ||12|| 
