.. mantravinyāsaḥ oṃ sarvadharmābhāvasvabhāvaviśuddhavana a ā aṃ aḥ prakṛtipari śuddhāḥ sarva dharmāḥ yaduta sarvatathāgatajñānakāyasya mañjuśrīpariśuddhitā mupādāyeti | ma āḥ sarvatathāgatahṛdaya hara hara oṃ hūṃ hrīṃ bhagavan jñāna mūrtivāgīśvaramahāvāca sarvadharmagaganāmala supariśuddhadharmadhātujñānagabhaṃ āḥ| 
iti mantravinyāsaḥ | oṃ sarvadharmābhāvasvabhāvaviśuddhavana a ā aṃ aḥ prakṛtipariśuddhāḥ sarvadharmāḥ, yaduta sarvatathāgatajñānakāyasya mañjuśrīpariśuddhitāmupādāyeti | a āḥ sarvatathāgatahṛdaya hara hara oṃ hūṁ hrīṃ bhagavan jñānamūrti( te) vāgīśvaramahāvāca sarvadharmagaganāmala supariśuddhadharmadhātujñānagarbha āḥ| .. ādimadhyāntādhiṣṭhāno’yaṃ mantraḥ | tathāhi bodhicittamakāraḥ, bhūmipāramitā caryāsvabhāvākāraḥ | buddhatvasūcakaḥ aṃkāraḥ| mahānirmā(ba)ṇadyotako akāraḥ| jñānakā yādhiṣṭhānaka ākāraḥ| kāyavāñcittarāgādhiṣṭhānakā oṃ hūṁ hrīṃkārāḥ dharmadhātu vāgīśvarātmaka(ka) sthiracalarūpāvasthitaparidharmakāyāḥ mudrārthaḥ mākāroṃ’nte vihita iti || 31 || 
