ityādi svānubhūtameva ca mārgamasaau prakāśitavān mumukṣūṇāmityasyāpi śabara guroviṣayaviṣayivyomāśleṣataḥ pravṛttāni nimittāni 'dhūmādīni vakṣyamāṇāni | atra pakṣe viṣayaviṣayivyomāśleṣe pravṛttaṃ nimittaṃ yasyeti vyutpattiḥ| punaḥ kiṃvidham ? ravītyādi| raviśaśitamasāmarkendurāhūṇāṃ vatsa(sma) padavīmāvṛtya vyāyasva jñāna dīptyā pracchāya| āśarārīti śarāḥ pañca arāḥ prakoṣṭhāni tataścāyamarthaḥ| pañca prakoṣṭhāni yasya tatpañcagatikaṃ saṃsāracakramasuraśataairdeveṣvantarbhāvāt| āsamantād vyāpya calā pracaradrūpā kriyā sattvārthakṛtyaṃ yasya| arkācā api divārātrikaraśubhā śubhasūcakāḥ sattvānāṃ kintu saṃsāriṇaḥ | asya śabarādhipasya tu lokottarārthakāritvam | punaḥ kiṃ rūpaṃ sphuranti ? dedīpyamānāḥ| ustarā mahattarā jñānajyotiṣaḥ, śrutiḥ gatiḥ prasaraṇaṃ yasmāttat | arkendroyotirasti na tu jñānajyotiḥ| ato arkādhā cchādanamanena 'tādṛśanāmārthagrahāyāhaḻūtānāmadhigamāsambhavāt | taduktam 
